text: Two-Buldi-Two () is a 1929 Soviet movie directed by Nina Agadzhanova and Lev Kuleshov.Биография Льва КулешоваДва-Бульди-два (1929) The movie tells the story of circus performers during the Civil War. It stars Sergey Komarov, Vladimir Kochetov, and Anel Sudakevich. == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Soviet silent movies Category:1929 movies Category:Movies directed by Lev Kuleshov
